exports[`skill.init.behavior.guards.journey given: [case1] full behavior route with guards when: [t0] vision pass attempted without promises then: blocked by unpromised self-review 1`] = `
"рҹӘЁ run solid skill repo=bhrain/role=driver/skill=route.stone.set

рҹҰү the way speaks for itself

рҹ—ҝ route.stone.set
   в”ңв”Җ stone = 1.vision
   в””в”Җ passage = blocked (review.self required)

рҹҢ• lets reflect
   в”Ӯ
   в”ңв”Җ review.self 1/8
   в”Ӯ  в”ңв”Җ slug = has-questioned-fundamentals
   в”Ӯ  в”ңв”Җ question all, especially yourself
   в”Ӯ  в””в”Җ see the guide below
   в”Ӯ
   в”ңв”Җ stillness рҹӘ·
   в”Ӯ  в”ңв”Җ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  so it is. a chance to slow down, breathe, and see clearly.
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  self review time is a sanctuary. a gift. a luxury not always available.
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  it is not every day one has a quiet moment to take a slow,
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  methodical, patient, and thorough review.
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  tea first. then, we proceed рҹҚө
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в””в”Җ
   в”Ӯ
   в”ңв”Җ before you begin рҹӘ·
   в”Ӯ  в”ңв”Җ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  - clear your mind. this is dedicated review time.
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  - open each artifact mentioned in the guide
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  - read through them slowly, line by line
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  - question every assumption made
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  - look with fresh eyes, as if for the first time
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в””в”Җ
   в”Ӯ
   в”ңв”Җ here's the guide
   в”Ӯ  в”ңв”Җ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  did we reason from first principles or from convention?
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ    for this vision, ask:
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ    - what are the fundamental truths here that we know are true?
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ    - do we build from those truths, or from "how it's usually done"?
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ    - if we started from scratch with only the fundamentals, what would we build?
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ    - what would this cost if we broke it down to raw materials/components?
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ    ensure we solve the right problem, not just the familiar one.
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в””в”Җ
   в”Ӯ
   в”ңв”Җ be here now рҹӘ·
   в”Ӯ  в”ңв”Җ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  refocus.
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  the review is the work.
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  not a step to complete.
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  not a gate to pass.
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  not a checkbox to check.
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  it is the work itself.
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  you do not care about the stone.
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  you only care about the review.
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в””в”Җ
   в”Ӯ
   в”ңв”Җ walk the way рҹӘ·
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в”ңв”Җ articulate into
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  в””в”Җ /review/self/for.1.vision._.r1.has-questioned-fundamentals.md
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в”ңв”Җ for each found issue рҹӘҳ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  в”ңв”Җ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  articulate how it was fixed
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  so you remember for next time
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ  в””в”Җ
   в”Ӯ  в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ  в””в”Җ for each non issue рҹӘҳ
   в”Ӯ     в”ңв”Җ
   в”Ӯ     в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ     в”Ӯ  articulate why it holds
   в”Ӯ     в”Ӯ  so others can learn from it
   в”Ӯ     в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ     в””в”Җ
   в”Ӯ
   в””в”Җ when you've truly reflected, run
      в””в”Җ rhx route.stone.set --stone 1.vision --as promised --that has-questioned-fundamentals[0m[31m[0m
[0m[31mрҹӘЁ run solid skill repo=bhrain/role=driver/skill=route.stone.set[0m
[0m[31m   в””в”Җ вңӢ blocked by constraints[0m
